{"id":"gizonite","term":"Gizonite","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A name given to Hashem, an inhabitant of Gizoh, a place somewhere in the mountains of Judah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 11:34\">1 Chr. 11:34</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 23:32\">2 Sam. 23:32</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 23:34\">34</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 11:34","2 Samuel 23:32","2 Samuel 23:34"]}